Package: nftables
Section: admin
Priority: required
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: libc (>= 1.1.8), ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: replaces the popular {ip,ip6,arp,eb}tables.
 nftables replaces the popular {ip,ip6,arp,eb}tables. This software provides 
 a new in-kernel packet classification framework that is based on a network-specific 
 Virtual Machine (VM) and a new nft userspace command line tool. 
 .
 nftables reuses the existing Netfilter subsystems such as the existing hook 
 infrastructure, the connection tracking system, NAT, userspace queueing and logging 
 subsystem. 

